headline: DuPont Announces Increase in Quarterly Dividend on Common Stock
summary: DuPont (NYSE: DD) today announced that its Board of Directors has declared a quarterly dividend of forty-one cents ($0.41) per share on the outstanding Common Stock (par value $0.01 per share), representing an 8% increase to its 2024 quarterly dividends, payable on March 17, 2025, to holders of record of said stock at the close of business on March 3, 2025.(1)

headline: DuPont Announces Appointment of Kurt McMaken to Board of Directors
summary: DuPont (NYSE: DD) today announced the appointment of Kurt McMaken to its Board of Directors, effective immediately. Mr. McMaken will serve on the Audit committee and Nomination and Governance committee.
